<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FuegoMail - Self-Hosted Email Marketing Platform</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 100px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0 0 40px 0;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .hero .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      background: white;
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .hero .cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .features {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .features h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .feature {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .feature h3 {
      color: #667eea;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }
    .feature p {
      color: #666;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .pricing {
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }
    .pricing h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .pricing-card {
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .pricing-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: #667eea;
    }
    .pricing-card.featured {
      border-color: #667eea;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
    }
    .pricing-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .pricing-card .price {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #667eea;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .pricing-card .price span {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #999;
    }
    .pricing-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .pricing-card ul li {
      padding: 10px 0;
      color: #666;
    }
    .pricing-card ul li:before {
      content: "âœ“ ";
      color: #667eea;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      opacity: 0.8;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>FuegoMail</h1>
      <p>Self-hosted email marketing platform powered by AWS SES</p>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "Go to Dashboard", authenticated_root_path, class: "cta" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "cta" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <div class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Choose FuegoMail?</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ðŸš€ Self-Hosted Control</h3>
          <p>Deploy on your own infrastructure. You own your data, you control your destiny. No vendor lock-in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ðŸ’° Cost-Effective</h3>
          <p>Leverage AWS SES pricing - pay only $0.10 per 1,000 emails. No monthly platform fees, no hidden costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ðŸ“Š Advanced Segmentation</h3>
          <p>Target your audience with powerful segmentation rules. Send the right message to the right people.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ðŸŽ¨ Beautiful Templates</h3>
          <p>Create stunning emails with our HTML and Markdown editor. Real-time preview shows exactly what subscribers see.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ðŸ“ˆ Real-Time Analytics</h3>
          <p>Track opens, clicks, bounces, and complaints. Comprehensive campaign statistics at your fingertips.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ðŸ”Œ RESTful API</h3>
          <p>Integrate with your existing tools. Full-featured API for subscribers, campaigns, lists, and more.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <div class="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Simple, Transparent Pricing</h2>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Free</h3>
          <div class="price">$0<span>/month</span></div>
          <ul>
            <li>500 subscribers</li>
            <li>2,500 emails/month</li>
            <li>1 list</li>
            <li>Basic templates</li>
            <li>Email support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card featured">
          <h3>Starter</h3>
          <div class="price">$0<span>/month</span></div>
          <ul>
            <li>5,000 subscribers</li>
            <li>25,000 emails/month</li>
            <li>Unlimited lists</li>
            <li>Custom templates</li>
            <li>Advanced segmentation</li>
            <li>Priority support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Pro</h3>
          <div class="price">$0<span>/month</span></div>
          <ul>
            <li>25,000 subscribers</li>
            <li>125,000 emails/month</li>
            <li>Unlimited lists</li>
            <li>Custom templates</li>
            <li>Advanced segmentation</li>
            <li>API access</li>
            <li>Priority support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Agency</h3>
          <div class="price">$0<span>/month</span></div>
          <ul>
            <li>Unlimited subscribers</li>
            <li>Unlimited emails</li>
            <li>Unlimited lists</li>
            <li>White-label options</li>
            <li>Multi-tenant support</li>
            <li>Dedicated support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; color: #666;">
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> FuegoMail is free to self-host. You only pay for AWS SES usage ($0.10 per 1,000 emails).</p>
        <p>Pricing tiers represent suggested usage limits and feature availability for different deployment scenarios.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> FuegoMail. Open-source email marketing platform.</p>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <%= link_to "Documentation", page_path("docs") %>
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <%= link_to "Dashboard", authenticated_root_path %>
          <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, data: { turbo_method: :delete } %>
        <% else %>
          <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path %>
          <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
